{
  "version": "3.0.0",
  "releaseNotes": {
    "zh": [
      "新增分页图片与长图导出，可保存到系统相册，并在生成记录中阅读、缩放和分享。",
      "重做 EPUB 流式排版并嵌入中英文字体，修复第三方阅读器中的标题挤压、强制居中和异常断词。",
      "新增智能调整顺序，按词条长度平衡各栏，减少页面留白和纸张浪费。",
      "导出文件名精确到秒，修复同一分钟内生成文件被覆盖的问题。",
      "macOS 使用 SwiftUI 原生导航与液态玻璃文档自定义窗口；其他平台同步优化动画和滑块性能。",
      "关闭首页文档自定义窗口后不再自动弹出键盘；官网同步更新五种导出介绍与更流畅的一次性动效。"
    ],
    "en": [
      "Added page-image and long-image export with Photos saving plus in-app reading, zooming, and sharing.",
      "Rebuilt EPUB with conservative reflow and embedded Chinese and Latin fonts for consistent third-party reading.",
      "Added Smart reorder to balance entry lengths across columns and reduce empty space and paper use.",
      "Export filenames now include seconds so books created in the same minute never overwrite each other.",
      "Moved macOS navigation and document customization into native SwiftUI with Liquid Glass, while optimizing dialog and slider performance on every platform.",
      "Fixed keyboard focus after closing customization and refreshed the website with five-format copy and purposeful one-shot motion."
    ]
  },
